{
  "stem": "8423.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, it was a phony address.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I don't remember it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Phony address-- Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- everything was phony.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was phony, because of course they had no intentions of bringing any of our things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was just so we wouldn't try to carry it on the freight car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We should leave everything behind, because there was no room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put 100 people into each freight car, 100.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, I always had a vision of the freight car being quite large, because so many of us were in there, until I went to Washington, where they happened to have at the Holocaust Museum a freight car, an actual freight car.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I saw it, I realized how small it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could not for the life of me-- I mean, I found the spot, you know, within this freight car, as compared to the freight car I was in, exactly where I was most of the time and so forth.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the car was so tiny that I just couldn't believe that 100 of us were in that car.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that's how they jammed us in, 100 to a car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were old and sick people, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No facilities.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They locked the doors the minute they jammed the 100 in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mean literally jammed us in like sardines, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Closed freight car with just a little tiny openings that they have for the animals, you know, for air on top.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would climb up on each other's shoulders, the children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would look out because the adults kept saying, see if you can see a sign.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See if you can see a station, you know, where there might be a sign, to see where we're going, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
